        "subject": "LU-2158 lvfs: Remove cruft from lvfs_linux.h",
        "message": "LU-2158 lvfs: Remove cruft from lvfs_linux.h\n\nVarious bits from the lvfs_linux.h file were removed as they are no\nlonger used. Specifically, the following was removed:\n\n * l_inode\n * lvfs_sbdev_sync\n * lvfs_set_rdonly\n * lvfs_clear_rdonly\n * lvfs_dentry_params\n\nChange-Id: I993a1416bb548746ca717904a483c0cd6245768e\nSigned-off-by: Prakash Surya <surya1@llnl.gov>\n"
      },
